{"tid":1551650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(物理) 中年婦華富邨墮樓 倒斃瀑布灣道一學校內","createTime":"2019-09-08T05:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:09:11.000Z","uid":103237,"like":175,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bd1639d428daddc62c492b8a081b0bbce9a50f","tid":1551650,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4xBCPMns64LE2Aj1XkBjaw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hk/hk01_725/90fb8f61a3fc8d689ec100258c3e85d6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4xBCPMns64LE2Aj1XkBjaw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fhk01_725%2F90fb8f61a3fc8d689ec100258c3e85d6&h=19662ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早（8日）6時08分，警方接獲一名女子報案，指發現其母親倒卧瀑布灣道一學校，懷疑其從高處墮下。警方接報到場，該名女子現場被證實死亡。警方經初步調查，相信香港仔華富邨華建樓從上址一走廊墮下，人員於現場檢獲遺書，事件無可疑，女子死因則有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ad/Rzutp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Fad%2FRzutp.gif&h=e38c69eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死者跌係學校車道(樓梯右邊)入面(目測大約離樓邊&gt;4米)<br />\n目測華建樓21層樓高<br />\n假設大約2.5米一層=離地52.5米<br />\n<br />\n根據projectile motion<br />\n落地時間 = 開方(52.5/0.5/9.81) = 3.27秒<br />\n水平速率 = 4/3.27 = 1.22 米/秒<br />\n<br />\n世界立定跳遠總距離都係3.71米<br />\n有冇物理撚可以睇下一個婦人係咪可以跌到咁遠?<br />\n<br />\nAnyway RIP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD-%E5%A9%A6%E4%BA%BA%E8%8F%AF%E5%AF%8C%E9%82%A8%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93-%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%8F%AD%E5%80%92%E6%96%83%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1-005136087.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25AF%258C%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%2580%2592%25E6%2596%2583%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%25A1-005136087.html&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=e4e1e5f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD-%E5%A9%A6%E4%BA%BA%E8%8F%AF%E5%AF%8C%E9%82%A8%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93-%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%8F%AD%E5%80%92%E6%96%83%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1-005136087.html</a>"},{"pid":"da9d80c6856b1c26d517f1847ba2abab203253a4","tid":1551650,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"Again?"},{"pid":"44dda726e444e549826480e41c3fdd0d8401b6d7","tid":1551650,"uid":293648,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"被墮樓?"},{"pid":"a6eb72a70662f353a2baf2c7b3ae1662bf408b5c","tid":1551650,"uid":68598,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"但佢個女報案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ad11a49ba42fea63556231fbe88ec0cec977ff","tid":1551650,"uid":285768,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過呢個問題<br />\n果度每次有人跳樓都係跌在欄外<br />\n<br />\n利申：華寶校友，住該區二十幾年"},{"pid":"c1ec32f6ac44b35d7ef9ed5bae81724e96f40766","tid":1551650,"uid":100772,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"好多被自殺案件"},{"pid":"272fe09ae91a4ad688b9e7fdf1592cb4af12f764","tid":1551650,"uid":268086,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"幾次自殺都係得01報？"},{"pid":"1808d480858b4fd771609df571fe97182ec57d22","tid":1551650,"uid":112581,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:02:08.000Z","msg":"咪膠 立定跳遠講緊同樣高度<br />\n你行路水平速度都差唔多1.2m/s"},{"pid":"b7854e67dfb2c902ca08ce3f6ba000ae7294d835","tid":1551650,"uid":143849,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"272fe09ae91a4ad688b9e